390
00:40:46,570 --> 00:40:48,260
Bullshit!

391
00:40:48,260 --> 00:40:50,660
Your Shuobo king is so shameless.

392
00:40:50,660 --> 00:40:53,500
He even thought of such an ugly trick.

393
00:40:53,500 --> 00:40:55,330
You want me to go back to Shuobo with you?

394
00:40:55,330 --> 00:40:57,390
No way!

395
00:41:02,970 --> 00:41:07,780
A slave is a slave. You prefer the harsh way?

396
00:41:07,780 --> 00:41:11,230
Men, attack!

397
00:41:15,520 --> 00:41:19,440
Don't kill the female! I want her alive!

398
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:21,160
Teacher!

399
00:42:04,770 --> 00:42:06,390
Teacher!

400
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:23,190
Xiaowu, take the princess away! We'll meet at Gongyue City.
("gongyue" means moon bow)

401
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:25,050
